title: OD: tentations au soleil
overview: OD: tentations au soleil takes flight on Crave with former single contestants from OCCUPATION DOUBLE known for their strong personalities. They take part in lascivious challenges, daring missions, and tropical getaways. Only one couple will return from this game of seduction with suitcases heavier by $25,000. Flirting, strategy, and bickering are to be expected!
